# Commit the useful stuff: raw generations (needed for sample-response tooltips)
# and the precomputed projection.json (what the live viz actually reads).
# Raw per-sample embeddings are ~30KB each and would bloat the repo to ~800MB
# at full scale. They can be regenerated from data/generations/ via pnpm harness,
# or rebuilt directly via OpenAI from the stored response text.
data/embeddings/
